text: Ooi Kah Yan (born 6 December 2000 in Seremban) is a Malaysian professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 109 in the world. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian female squash players Category:People from Negeri Sembilan Category:Southeast Asian Games medalists in squash Category:Southeast Asian Games gold medalists for Malaysia Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games
